  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/be9956252154eb2fff95792cb0f94688.poster.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/be9956252154eb2fff95792cb0f94688.webm?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/be9956252154eb2fff95792cb0f94688.mp4?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Players take on the role of an Assassin and must find five hidden ninjas. <br>　Click on the suspicious places to make the world move and clear😇. <br>　The story? You'll have to make up for that with your imagination and spunk. <br>　That's the privilege of being human and a living being. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/df9205163dd0beb98b48491ca8895d02.poster.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/df9205163dd0beb98b48491ca8895d02.webm?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/df9205163dd0beb98b48491ca8895d02.mp4?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　The world of Makibishi Comic is full of gimmicks. <br>　What? Gimmicks are too absurd? <br>　The real world is much more absurd 😤. <br>　Taxes when you live, taxes when you die. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜Tell me! Mr. Rabbit's World Explained＞</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/5aa7258ff79c53fbcad262e43381e340.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　You'll see a lot of ennui and unique characters! <br>　And they make the world go round. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/999f1b17227cca299ab0f1a2952837ff.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=816 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Let me tell you two good things. <br>　1.\"It's dangerous to go alone! Take this.\" <br>　2.\"All your base are belong to us.\"  <br>　3.\"Thank you Mario! But our princess is in another castle!\"  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜Game Guide＞</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　We have created a strategy site.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　You can find it somewhere on the official website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/be9956252154eb2fff95792cb0f94688.poster.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/be9956252154eb2fff95792cb0f94688.webm?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/be9956252154eb2fff95792cb0f94688.mp4?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Players take on the role of an Assassin and must find five hidden ninjas. <br>　Click on the suspicious places to make the world move and clear😇. <br>　The story? You'll have to make up for that with your imagination and spunk. <br>　That's the privilege of being human and a living being. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/df9205163dd0beb98b48491ca8895d02.poster.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/df9205163dd0beb98b48491ca8895d02.webm?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/df9205163dd0beb98b48491ca8895d02.mp4?t=1762427316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　The world of Makibishi Comic is full of gimmicks. <br>　What? Gimmicks are too absurd? <br>　The real world is much more absurd 😤. <br>　Taxes when you live, taxes when you die. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜Tell me! Mr. Rabbit's World Explained＞</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/5aa7258ff79c53fbcad262e43381e340.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　You'll see a lot of ennui and unique characters! <br>　And they make the world go round. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/999f1b17227cca299ab0f1a2952837ff.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=816 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Let me tell you two good things. <br>　1.\"It's dangerous to go alone! Take this.\" <br>　2.\"All your base are belong to us.\"  <br>　3.\"Thank you Mario! But our princess is in another castle!\"  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844530/extras/ed25ed169df8afd3f7a3a44154b10ce5.avif?t=1762427316\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜Game Guide＞</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　We have created a strategy site.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　You can find it somewhere on the official website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img